snippet.title: Moonfang _ Trailer
snippet.description:
Moonfang is a puzzle game for IOS, Android and PC.
Guiding three characters, your goal is to flee the city you are in, escaping the sight of every person searching for you. Beware! The moon will reveal the animalistic power of your heroes!
https://moonfang-game.com/
